result.name: Tam Chai Yunnan Noodles

reviews.text: Located in the Port Centre, it is a very famous Yunnan rice noodle restaurant. It offers Yunnan rice noodles, snacks and drinks. Yunnan rice noodles is a featured dishes with very rich ingredients. It is delicious, worth recommending. Among all the snacks, the bandit chicken wings ( 土匪雞翼 ) are the most popular. It is crisp and spicy, everyone loves it. The soup may have added MSG, so the next time you eat rice noodles, remember do not drink the soups.
Typical Chinese food and very common in HK. Price is reasonable.
Must eat: white-boiled meat with smashed garlic 蒜泥白肉
A place good for you to have a quick lunch and dinner. But this is not the traditional noodle of Hong Kong.
Not so good.. food quality is not steady.. service is so so .. unfortunately not so many choices in this area that’s why I am still eating in this restaurant occasionally

reviews.text: Located in the Port Centre, it is a very famous Yunnan rice noodle restaurant. It offers Yunnan rice noodles, snacks and drinks. Yunnan rice noodles is a featured dishes with very rich ingredients. It is delicious, worth recommending. Among all the snacks, the bandit chicken wings ( 土匪雞翼 ) are the most popular. It is crisp and spicy, everyone loves it. The soup may have added MSG, so the next time you eat rice noodles, remember do not drink the soups.
這間連鎖米線店是本人最常去的其中一間食品店，價格環境都比較好。唯一就是午餐時間很多人排隊。
店員沒禮貌，阿嬸好串，擺明趕客，駁你嘴俾你加料真係無人敢食
衹感覺味精好重、而又座得貼、又嘈、價錢又唔平、有D失望
Typical Chinese food and very common in HK. Price is reasonable.
